    <item>
      <title>特朗普政策不确定性下，降息有望推动菲律宾股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/rate-cut-seen-to-power-philippine-stocks-amid-trump-uncertainty</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾证券交易所负责人周四表示，在唐纳德·特朗普政策存在不确定性的情况下，再次将政策利率下调四分之一个百分点将有助于菲律宾股市复苏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/rate-cut-seen-to-power-philippine-stocks-amid-trump-uncertainty</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 04:04:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国起诉、取消债券发售后阿达尼股价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/adani-bonds-tumble-after-founder-charged-by-us-authorities</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国检察官指控创始人高塔姆·阿达尼参与贿赂阴谋后，阿达尼集团旗下子公司的股票和债券大幅下跌。该集团还取消了 6 亿美元的债券发售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/adani-bonds-tumble-after-founder-charged-by-us-authorities</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 00:53:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
